中國領土的謬誤<br />\n(2) 中英聯合聲明的謬誤<br />\n(3) 不平等條約無效論是謊言<br />\n(4) 中華民國早已放棄香港的主權<br />\n(5) 中華人民共和國以武力脅迫大英國移交香港主權不合國際法<br />\n(6) 70年代聯合國從非自治領名單剔除香港<br />\n(7) 中英聯合聲明違反住民自決原則<br />\n(8) 香港符合《蒙特維多國家權利及義務公約》中「國家」的定義<br />\n(9) 香港軍事史<br />\n<br />\n請幫推以下post！<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"color: violet;\">香港人一定要知！</span></ins></strong></span></span>一定一定要睇！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">香港史實在此！勿做港豬！想贏就入嚟！</span></span></span></span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"9e7e6394bd23dbfef3984e43e51b921a3025b651","tid":1545081,"uid":284940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T03:14:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">判林鄭落地獄<br />\n光復香港秩序</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qc1S47m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQc1S47m.jpg&h=52f5d3de&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c9c9461fc45b1483c59414ff0e064967e945a04a","tid":1545081,"uid":7832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T03:21:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa96d16056afa5e343ca249587ed7a585cd8f498","tid":1545081,"uid":283972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T18:17:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b60125d83dfcecf4b8d53d10ac7eb74fccc0a036","tid":1545081,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T00:31:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3269649f0fa9654097721bd620f02d7